## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **paltusotine 2025 (Crinetics, projected first FDA)** = first non-peptide oral SSTR2 selective agonist. PATHFNDR-1+2 Phase 3 2024 IGF-1 normalization 효과 확인. peptide SST IM/SC monthly 패러다임에서 oral daily 로의 paradigm shift. quantum-VQE 의 non-peptide GPCR pocket 직접 fit.
2. **octreotide capsule Mycapssa 2020** = first FDA oral somatostatin analog. peptide + permeation enhancer 기반 maintenance 적응증. compliance 향상 + 만성 IM/SC injection 회피. 그러나 절대 bioavailability 한정 + paltusotine 2025 후 시장 변화 예상.
3. **pegvisomant Somavert 2003** = first FDA GH receptor antagonist. PEGylated mutant GH (B2036) — receptor dimerization 차단. IGF-1 정상화 효과 우수, 그러나 daily SC + 비용 + 만성 종양 자체 미축소. quantum-VQE 의 receptor dimerization geometry 가 explicit modeling 가능.
4. **pasireotide LAR Signifor LAR 2014** = third SST analog, multi-receptor SSTR1/2/3/5. octreotide/lanreotide 무반응 acromegaly 의 second-line. 부작용 hyperglycemia (SSTR5 pancreatic β-cell). 2014 Cushing 적응증 cross-link.
5. **octreotide LAR (1998) + lanreotide depot (2007) + pasireotide LAR (2014)** = SST analog 3-세대. monthly IM/SC 가 30년간 paradigm. paltusotine (2025) 가 첫 oral non-peptide 로 paradigm 종료 가능성.
6. **cabergoline + bromocriptine** = DA D2 agonist first-line in mild-moderate acromegaly + co-secreting GH/PRL adenoma. prolactinoma cross-link distinct (95%+ prolactinoma response vs 10-30% acromegaly response).
7. **transsphenoidal surgery (TSS)** = 만성 1L 표준 (microadenoma 80%+ remission, macroadenoma 50% remission). post-surgery medical therapy 가 SST/GH-R/DA 의 적응증.
8. **stereotactic radiosurgery (SRS) + fractionated RT** = refractory + recurrent 보조. long-latency hypopituitarism + 시신경 위험. 5-10년 latency 까지 IGF-1 정상화 효과.
9. **temozolomide off-label aggressive/atypical pituitary** = MGMT-low pituitary carcinoma + aggressive pituitary 의 last-resort. 적응증 외 사용 + 기준 RCT 없음.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, acromegaly 임상 의미 한정. paltusotine PATHFNDR-1+2 (Crinetics 2024 readout) 가 외부 임상 검증 의존.

